platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Whether you just want to get away or totally forgot to reserve a room, Hotel Tonight proves that last-minute accommodations don’t have to be last resorts. By unearthing unsold rooms, this helpful app can offer some steep savings. A streamlined interface puts photos in the forefront, and when you’re ready to book, it’s as simple as could be. Bring on the spontaneous trips!
